data.description: Charming traditional home with an open concept and 4 bedrooms. This home is a must-see with luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the main floor and stairs! Beautifully remodeled kitchen with quartz counters, full height backsplash, undermount large sink, stainless steel gas appliances, and built-in desk. Cozy family room with gas fireplace and abundant natural light. Master bedroom with walk-in closet and remodeled private bath. Fully fenced backyard with a patio. New Furnace, AC, floors, carpets, painted cabinets, and dishwasher. Prime location near intel, shopping, and restaurants! [Home Energy Score = 4. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10221507]
